# Output encoding (mobile analogs)

Source: **`owasp_secure_coding_hardening_plan.md`** Phase 6; helpers **`GoDivePlainText`**, **`GoDiveRemoteURLPolicy`**.

## Do

- Render user / API strings with **`Text(stringVar)`** or **`Text(verbatim:)`** — never **`Text("…\(untrusted)")`** (`LocalizedStringKey` Markdown).
- Gate remote catalog image URLs with **`GoDiveRemoteURLPolicy.sanitizedCatalogImageURL`** before **`AsyncImage`**.
- Gate USDZ / Storage downloads with **`GoDiveRemoteURLPolicy.sanitizedCatalogDownloadURL`** (Firebase / CDN hosts only).
- Share / export as plain text or PNG; XML-escape if a UDDF/CSV writer is added later.
- Trip share temp files: UUID filenames under the system temp directory (**`TripShareTempFilePolicy`**).

## Do not

- Render dive notes / site names / Fishial names as Markdown or HTML.
- Add **`WKWebView`** / **`loadHTMLString`** of user content without a new security review.
- Embed raw user notes into XML/UDDF/CSV without escaping.
- Load `http://`, `file://`, localhost, or IP-literal catalog asset URLs.
